# Formatted

```scss
@import "theme";

@import "rounded-corners", "text-shadow";

@import "theme.scss", "spacing";

@import "theme.css" print;

@import "print.css" print, "spacing";

@import "print.css" print, screen;

@import url("theme.css");

```
